{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "17bbcf2d-91f4-4233-bf98-7ed61fa483d6", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/17bbcf2d-91f4-4233-bf98-7ed61fa483d6@2.pkg/1772602142586/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602143360", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/17bbcf2d-91f4-4233-bf98-7ed61fa483d6@2.pkg/1772602142586/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602143360"}, "identifier": "17bbcf2d-91f4-4233-bf98-7ed61fa483d6", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>这一年暮春，长安城中车水马龙，热闹非凡。原来是到了牡丹盛开的时节，长安城里的名门大户纷纷相随前去买花。牡丹花的价钱贵贱不一，价钱多少以花的品种来定。这里的牡丹有的枝繁叶茂，鲜红欲滴，小小的束花，要付五捆白绢的价钱。它们被精心呵护着，主人还给张上了帷幕，筑起了樊篱。辛勤浇灌之余还培上了最肥沃的土，因此花的颜色还和以前一样鲜艳。家家习以为俗，更没有人认为是错的。有一个老农，无意中也来到了买花的地方。目睹此情景，不由得低头长叹，然而此叹又有谁在意呢：这一丛深色的牡丹花，价钱相当于十户中等人家一年的赋税了。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D.&ldquo;《卖炭翁》以&lsquo;夜来城外一尺雪'与'晓驾炭车辗冰辙&rsquo;对比&rdquo;有误。《卖炭翁》以&ldquo;一车炭，千余斤&rdquo;与&ldquo;半匹红纱一丈绫&rdquo;对比，反映出&ldquo;宫市&rdquo;掠夺的残酷。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读选文，回答相关问题。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>甲 卖炭翁</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">伐薪烧炭南山中，满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑。卖炭得钱何所营?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">身上衣裳口中食。可怜身上衣正单，心忧炭贱愿天寒。夜来城外一尺雪，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">晓驾炭车辗冰辙。牛困人饥日已高，市南门外泥中歇。翩翩两骑来是谁?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">黄衣使者白衫儿。手把文书口称敕，回车叱牛牵向北。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">一车炭，千余斤，宫使驱将惜不得。半匹红纱一丈绫，系向牛头充炭直。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>乙 &nbsp;送买花（白居易）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;帝城</span><span><sup>①</sup></span><span>春欲暮，喧喧车马度。共道牡丹时，相随买花去。贵贱无常价，酬直看花数。灼灼百朵红，戋戋</span><span><sup>②</sup></span><span>五束素。上张幄幕庇，旁织巴篱护。水洒复泥封，移来色如故。家家习为俗，人人迷不悟。有一田舍翁，偶来买花处。低头独长叹，此叹无人喻。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;一丛深色花</span><span><sup>③</sup></span><span>，十户中人</span><span><sup>④</sup></span><span>赋！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【注释】①帝城：皇帝居住的城市，指长安。②戋（jiān）戋：细小，微少的样子。③深色花：指红牡丹。④中人：即中户，中等人家。唐代按户口征收赋税，分为上中下三等。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对下面两首古诗分析不正确的一项 （　　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "阅读选文，回答相关问题。甲 卖炭翁伐薪烧炭南山中，满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑。卖炭得钱何所营?身上衣裳口中食。可怜身上衣正单，心忧炭贱愿天寒。夜来城外一尺雪，晓驾炭车辗冰辙。牛困人饥日已高，市南门外泥中歇。翩翩两骑来是谁?黄衣使者白衫儿。手把文书口称敕，回车叱牛牵向北。一车炭，千余斤，宫使驱将惜不得。半匹红纱一丈绫，系向牛头充炭直。乙  送买花（白居易）    帝城①春欲暮，喧喧车马度。共道牡", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/17bbcf2d-91f4-4233-bf98-7ed61fa483d6@2.pkg/item.json?v=1747212928391", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《卖炭翁》中的&ldquo;辗&rdquo;字既写出路面结冰，天气寒冷，也写出牛车的重量，表现了卖炭翁的辛苦和勤劳。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《买花》前十四句写京城贵族买花，后六句写田舍翁感叹买花。全诗行文晓畅，讽刺辛辣，具有较深的社会意义。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《卖炭翁》中伐薪烧炭的卖炭翁受欺凌受压榨却不敢反抗；《买花》中田舍翁偶尔才来买花的地方，低头长叹是因为他无法理解达官贵族的生活方式。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>两首诗都运用了对比的手法：《卖炭翁》以&ldquo;夜来城外一尺雪&rdquo;与&ldquo;晓驾炭车辗冰辙&rdquo;对比，反映出&ldquo;宫市&rdquo;掠夺的残酷；《买花》把&ldquo;一丛&rdquo;花与&ldquo;十户&rdquo;赋等同起来，揭露了封建社会达官贵人挥霍人民血汗、纵情享乐的事实。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读选文，回答相关问题。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>甲 卖炭翁</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">伐薪烧炭南山中，满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑。卖炭得钱何所营?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">身上衣裳口中食。可怜身上衣正单，心忧炭贱愿天寒。夜来城外一尺雪，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">晓驾炭车辗冰辙。牛困人饥日已高，市南门外泥中歇。翩翩两骑来是谁?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">黄衣使者白衫儿。手把文书口称敕，回车叱牛牵向北。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">一车炭，千余斤，宫使驱将惜不得。半匹红纱一丈绫，系向牛头充炭直。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>乙 &nbsp;送买花（白居易）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;帝城</span><span><sup>①</sup></span><span>春欲暮，喧喧车马度。共道牡丹时，相随买花去。贵贱无常价，酬直看花数。灼灼百朵红，戋戋</span><span><sup>②</sup></span><span>五束素。上张幄幕庇，旁织巴篱护。水洒复泥封，移来色如故。家家习为俗，人人迷不悟。有一田舍翁，偶来买花处。低头独长叹，此叹无人喻。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;一丛深色花</span><span><sup>③</sup></span><span>，十户中人</span><span><sup>④</sup></span><span>赋！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【注释】①帝城：皇帝居住的城市，指长安。②戋（jiān）戋：细小，微少的样子。③深色花：指红牡丹。④中人：即中户，中等人家。唐代按户口征收赋税，分为上中下三等。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对下面两首古诗分析不正确的一项 （　　）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "17bbcf2d-91f4-4233-bf98-7ed61fa483d6", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "阅读选文，回答相关问题。甲 卖炭翁伐薪烧炭南山中，满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑。卖炭得钱何所营?身上衣裳口中食。可怜身上衣正单，心忧炭贱愿天寒。夜来城外一尺雪，晓驾炭车辗冰辙。牛困人饥日已高，市南门外泥中歇。翩翩两骑来是谁?黄衣使者白衫儿。手把文书口称敕，回车叱牛牵向北。一车炭，千余斤，宫使驱将惜不得。半匹红纱一丈绫，系向牛头充炭直。乙  送买花（白居易）    帝城①春欲暮，喧喧车马度。共道牡"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读选文，回答相关问题。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>甲 卖炭翁</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">伐薪烧炭南山中，满面尘灰烟火色，两鬓苍苍十指黑。卖炭得钱何所营?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">身上衣裳口中食。可怜身上衣正单，心忧炭贱愿天寒。夜来城外一尺雪，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">晓驾炭车辗冰辙。牛困人饥日已高，市南门外泥中歇。翩翩两骑来是谁?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">黄衣使者白衫儿。手把文书口称敕，回车叱牛牵向北。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;\">一车炭，千余斤，宫使驱将惜不得。半匹红纱一丈绫，系向牛头充炭直。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: center;\"><span>乙 &nbsp;送买花（白居易）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;帝城</span><span><sup>①</sup></span><span>春欲暮，喧喧车马度。共道牡丹时，相随买花去。贵贱无常价，酬直看花数。灼灼百朵红，戋戋</span><span><sup>②</sup></span><span>五束素。上张幄幕庇，旁织巴篱护。水洒复泥封，移来色如故。家家习为俗，人人迷不悟。有一田舍翁，偶来买花处。低头独长叹，此叹无人喻。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.19in;text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;一丛深色花</span><span><sup>③</sup></span><span>，十户中人</span><span><sup>④</sup></span><span>赋！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【注释】①帝城：皇帝居住的城市，指长安。②戋（jiān）戋：细小，微少的样子。③深色花：指红牡丹。④中人：即中户，中等人家。唐代按户口征收赋税，分为上中下三等。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对下面两首古诗分析不正确的一项 （　　）</span></p></div>"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/17bbcf2d-91f4-4233-bf98-7ed61fa483d6@2.pkg/1772602142586/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602143360", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/17bbcf2d-91f4-4233-bf98-7ed61fa483d6@2.pkg/1772602142586/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602143360"}, "auto_fill_thumb": true, "prom_resouce_type": "questions", "audit_teacher_ids": ["65a5d65a-1ba7-44c5-b0a4-9f09d3aa2474"], "copyright_holder_ids": [], "audit_status": "AUDIT_WAITING", "sys_resource_space": 197264, "qb_qu_num": 3, "res_sort": 202504212203203, "produce_type": "artificiality", "sys_packing_status": "ready", "qb_year": "2025", "nature": "tm_sync", "version_source_id": "17bbcf2d-91f4-4233-bf98-7ed61fa483d6", "format": "2d641585-d91b-4d65-8f5a-2a7fd8103ac7", "faculty_advisor_ids": ["0d011f6a-8dcb-4adb-8f5b-13c5783254be"